  <description>
    <facet>
      <vocabularyID>LRE.expressionDescriptionFacetValues</vocabularyID>
      <value>main</value>
    </facet>
    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206689</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Virtual Jamestown</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Virtuelles Jamestown</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Jamestown Virtuel</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Jamestown Virtual</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Jamestown Virtuale</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εικονικό Jamestown</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Jamestown Virtual</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">provides an open doorway to explore the history of the Jamestown settlement. The site features historical documents including laws, census data, contracts, state papers, maps, contemporary writings, and art.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">stellt einen geöffneten Eingang zur Verfügung, 
um die Geschichte der Jamestown Regelung zu erforschen. Die 
historischen Dokumente der Situationsmerkmale einschließlich Gesetze,
Zählungdaten, Verträge, Zustandpapiere, Karten, zeitgenössische 
Schreiben und kunst.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">fournit une porte ouverte pour explorer l'histoire
du règlement de Jamestown. Les documents historiques de 
dispositifs de site comprenant des lois, des données de recensement, 
des contrats, des papiers d'état, des cartes, des écritures 
contemporaines, et l'art.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">fornece uma entrada aberta para explorar o history
do estabelecimento de Jamestown. Os originais históricos das 
características de local including leis, dados de census, contratos, 
papéis do estado, mapas, escritas contemporary, e arte.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">fornisce una porta aperta per esplorare la storia 
dello stabilimento di Jamestown. I documenti storici delle 
caratteristiche di luogo compreso le leggi, i dati censuali, 
contratti, dichiarano le carte, i programmi, le scritture 
contemporanee e l'arte.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">παρέχει μια ανοικτή πόρτα για να ερευνήσει την 
ιστορία της τακτοποίησης Jamestown. Η περιοχή 
χαρακτηρίζει τα ιστορικά έγγραφα συμπεριλαμβανομένων των νόμων, 
των στοιχείων απογραφής, των συμβάσεων, των κρατικών εγγράφων, 
των χαρτών, των σύγχρονων γραφών, και της τέχνης.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">proporciona a un umbral abierto para explorar la 
historia del establecimiento de Jamestown. Los documentos 
históricos de las características de sitio incluyendo leyes, datos 
de censo, contratos, papeles del estado, correspondencias, escrituras 
contemporáneas, y arte.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
        </general>

    </metadata>
  </description>
